## 5. Static Analysis

### 5.1 ArchUnit (Architecture Tests)

**Purpose:** Enforce hexagonal architecture boundaries at compile time.

**Rules enforced:**
- Domain layer CANNOT depend on infrastructure (Spring, JPA)
- Domain layer CANNOT depend on application layer
- Application layer CANNOT depend on infrastructure
- GraphQL resolvers MUST call application services (not repositories)
- No cyclic dependencies between modules

**Run architecture tests:**
```bash
mvn test -Dtest=ArchitectureTest
```

**Example violation:**
```java
// ❌ BAD: Domain entity with JPA annotations
@Entity
public class User {
    @Id @GeneratedValue
    private Long id;
}
```

```java
// ✅ GOOD: Pure domain entity
public class User {
    private final UserId id;
    // ...
}
```

